data.description: Ask about incentives: Can be used towards 2/1 buy down, Closing costs or Landscape. Welcome to 7241 Rex Rd. This stunning home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, TRIPLE car garage, boasting over 3,000 sqft, on a 0.39 acre lot, With a Sun Room and MORE. Covered front porch, Open foyer with a formal dining room, Eat in kitchen with an oversized island perfect for entertaining, First floor guest bedroom W/ Full bathroom, Open floor plan and a huge walk in pantry. Upstairs you'll find a beautiful master oasis including a spacious stand up shower, large tub, dual vanity sinks and two huge walk in closets. You'll find 3 additional bedrooms and bonus room with endless use. A perfect find with ample space in a charming community nestled outside the city limits of Holly Springs. Convenient location to school, shops and parks. Community includes 7 Acre Lake, Pool, Soccer Field, Walking trails W/ a very active community. Includes a transferable home warranty. 11 Minutes from Downtown Holly Springs and 15 Minutes from Downtown Fuquay. A Perfect meeting point. USDA ELIGIBLE!!! No City taxes. Come check it out for yourself!!!
